text: The National Conference Students' Union (NCSU) is the student wing of the Jammu & Kashmir National Conference party, established on 21 July 2012. The organisation was founded by Omar Abdullah working president of the National Conference. ==See also== * Jammu & Kashmir National Conference * Jammu & Kashmir Youth National Conference * List of political parties ==References== ==External links== * official Jammu and Kashmir National Conference website Category:Student wings of political parties in India
title: National Conference Students' Union
